des: "We included our own measurements but you can vary them if you like!"
ins: Sprinkle coconut evenly on a sheet of waxed paper.  In a medium bowl, stir together marshmallows, graham cracker crumbs, condensed milk, walnuts and cherries.  Shape into a log.  Place on waxed paper and roll in coconut.  Wrap with waxed paper and refrigerate until firm.
